# Auth Service (Limen)

Thin auth service built on [Limen](https://limenauth.dev/) — replaces the custom JWT/JWKS auth stack.

## Stack

| Piece | Tech |
|-------|------|
| Library | `github.com/thecodearcher/limen` + plugins |
| HTTP | `net/http` (Limen handler mounted at `/auth/`) |
| Port | **8000** (HTTP only — no gRPC) |
| DB | PostgreSQL schema `auth` (Limen tables) |
| Events | NATS (`auth.user.created`, `email.send`) |
| Session | Opaque cookie + Bearer (`WithBearerEnabled`) |

## Plugins

- `credential-password` (username support, password reset, email verify)
- `oauth` + `oauth-google` + `oauth-facebook`
- Custom TikTok provider: `internal/oauth/tiktok` (Login Kit — `client_key` / `client_secret`)

## Layout

```
app/auth/
├── cmd/auth/main.go
├── configs/config.yaml
├── migrations/001_limen_schema.up.sql
├── internal/config/
├── internal/events/
└── internal/oauth/tiktok/
```

## Key endpoints

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `/auth/*` | Limen handler (signin/signup/oauth/me/signout/…) |
| `GET /internal/session` | Cluster introspect for other Go services (Bearer) |
| `GET /healthz` | Health |

## Other services

`pkg/auth` validates `Authorization: Bearer <opaque>` by calling
`GET {auth_service_url}/internal/session` (in-memory cache ~60s).
`JWTValidator` is a type alias for `SessionValidator` (Wire compatibility).

## Config / secrets

| Env | Notes |
|-----|-------|
| `LIMEN_SECRET` | Exactly 32 bytes — cluster secret `auth-limen-secret` |
| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID` / `GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET` | |
| `FACEBOOK_CLIENT_ID` / `FACEBOOK_CLIENT_SECRET` | |
| `TIKTOK_CLIENT_KEY` / `TIKTOK_CLIENT_SECRET` | TikTok Login Kit naming |
| OAuth credentials | Cluster secret `auth-oauth-credentials` (not in git) |

OAuth callbacks: `{BaseURL}/auth/oauth/{google|facebook|tiktok}/callback`

Production BaseURL: `https://api.puchi.io.vn`

## Local

```bash
# apply migrations/001_limen_schema.up.sql to Postgres (search_path=auth)
export LIMEN_SECRET="$(openssl rand -base64 24 | head -c 32)"
cd app/auth && go run ./cmd/auth/ -conf ../../configs
```

## Không còn (đã xoá)

JWT RS256 / JWKS, magic-link, TOTP MFA, RBAC trong auth-service, Valkey session store tùy chỉnh.
